  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: left;"><span>All apartments have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking), bath with shower head attachment or shower room, WC, flat screen cable / satellite TV with English speaking channels, kitchenette equipped with 4 hobs, microwave, oven, fridge, dishwasher, kitchenware, Nespresso coffee machine, kettle, food blender, toaster, food steamer, WiFi, towels, toiletries, bath robes (additional charge), hair dryer and all have a balcony. </span></p>
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">Two room apartment (A4): sleeps 2-4 people (35m²). Living room with double sofa bed and one twin/double bedroom </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Three room apartment (B6): sleeps 3-6 people (50m²). Living room with double sofa bed and two twin/double bedrooms </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Four room duplex apartment (C8): sleeps 4-8 people (70m²). Living room with double sofa bed and three twin/double bedrooms </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Four room cabin apartment (D0): sleeps 5-10 people (85m²). Living room with double sofa bed and three twin/double bedrooms, cabin with bunk beds suitable for children (between 6-14 yrs)</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><span>Five room duplex apartment (E0): sleeps 5-10 people (85m²). Living room with double sofa bed and four twin/double bedrooms </span></li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span>Beds are made up on arrival (except sofa beds) and end of stay cleaning is included (except kitchen area).</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
